session.content: Hello! I'm glad you're reaching out. How can I assist you today? I'm here to listen and help in the best way possible. Can you tell me more about what's been going on with your health recently? Let's start by discussing any symptoms, their severity, when they started, and if there are any specific concerns or triggers that make them worse. This will help me better understand how I can offer support. If there's anything else you feel is important to mention, please don't hesitate to share.

triage.reason: No red flags found; symptoms appear non-urgent.
